<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٦٢٩ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5442">ابْنُ أَبِي عَدِيٍّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">سُلَيْمَانَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4490">عَلْقَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَمَّا نَزَلَتْ: ﴿وَلَمْ يَلْبِسُوا إِيمَانَهُمْ بِظُلْمٍ﴾ قَالَ أَصْحَابُهُ: وَأَيُّنَا لَمْ يَظْلِمْ؟<span class="c5"> فَنَزَلَتْ:</span> ﴿إِنَّ الشِّرْكَ لَظُلْمٌ عَظِيمٌ﴾»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>